<BaseLayout title="Chronological Bible Plan" backLink="/" backText="Home" accentColor="#d97706">

    <div class="header" style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        <h1 style="font-size: 2.8rem; color: #d97706; margin: 0 0 10px 0;">Chronological Bible Plan</h1>
        <p style="color: #cbd5e1; font-size: 1.1rem;">Experience the grand story of Scripture in the order it actually happened.</p>
    </div>

    <div style="background: rgba(217, 119, 6, 0.1); border-left: 4px solid #d97706; padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 0 12px 12px 0; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        <p style="margin: 0; color: #fdf6e3; line-height: 1.5; font-size: 1.05rem;"><strong>1-Year Plan:</strong> These readings are compiled according to recent historical research. If the schedule provided is followed, the entire Bible will be read in one calendar year!</p>
    </div>

